[SN]TITLE[SN]
Have you ever wanted to make your own console?

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
From Playstation, to Xbox there are lots of different types of consoles out there, but what about one you have to make yourself?

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
20 June 2017 Last updated at 09:03 BST
The Makerbuino is a new handheld games console which you have to build yourself.
The console comes in lots of pieces and people have to put it together and code the games themselves in order to play it.
It was made by an 18-year-old inventor called Albert Gajsak, and he hopes it will encourage kids to want to build their own electronic devices.
Ricky has been finding out more...
